{"tid":36972,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後唔受得就咪做服務業啦！待人處事有問題！","createTime":"2016-12-13T05:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T22:53:18.000Z","uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4673836c262778d6df97bcf9bea0d5a8af791910","tid":36972,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"講起我就扯火啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一路都在太古廣場一間名店買衫，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間店有好多有錢人同名人幫襯，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有隻90後已經做了很多年，已經是senior，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多年黎都好俾心機做，經理亦好like佢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為收入不錯又隱定，隻90後原本諗住同拍拖多年既bf結婚，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多年黎佢好少俾人投訴，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且同好多大客既關係都唔錯，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排我再去間店幫襯，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢開頭已經好有禮貌介紹d新貨俾我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲話俾折頭我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我就無乜反應（想佢唔好煩我），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我望一望另一堆客，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果堆客係大陸人，三至四個，講野好大聲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講話可唔可以關左間鋪一陣，等佢揀衫，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢同我講，佢公司一向唔俾佢地咁做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n驚做壞個頭，除非真係有乜大人物，好多記者好混亂先可以咁做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但佢見到我黑口黑面，都識做話打電話去問一問老闆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老闆梗係話唔得啦，至多俾多d折頭我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就發老脾，鬧到隻90後一面屁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話我買野既錢多過我隻90後搵幾年既錢啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢知我係邊個唔敢得罪我，一味道歉，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住小妹就走左人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家d 90後連基本待人處事都唔識！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9153c16c8780668d3db027f23cbaa881621540de","tid":36972,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e3beeb6bc56f9105d97ff049192bf4f46da4f1","tid":36972,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"028867570ba8993c833377f2e157353107473c63","tid":36972,"uid":43665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16bebd68cee07481c9b1f8d344cf937f06e8dd7","tid":36972,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"樓主頒獎禮攞錯獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bbe42e958aba02388367a74ebd098300eab837","tid":36972,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"關豬腦"},{"pid":"693a1c391eeca53100f669ce57e5d2b74804c512","tid":36972,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"90後真係好垃圾<br />\n唔敢想像香港由呢班人話事<br />\n真係要幫手睇多香港幾年<br />\n唔可以退休"},{"pid":"b3279ea39bcc170b1c869bfd6ad2390bd0e1716d","tid":36972,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"唔係針對幾多十後"},{"pid":"31692e50c61b0edeec3485b784553a670c7eb667","tid":36972,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係針對幾多十後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條友真係90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee27c0c3eeed761074d1a1857dc9992f5dc9c99","tid":36972,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係針對幾多十後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條友真係90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持樓豬搞到90後冇咗份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c474ef1c3fcd10198f268cba09cc5ffdfea33f","tid":36972,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係針對幾多十後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條友真係90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持樓豬搞到90後冇咗份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗緊投唔投訴佢好"},{"pid":"b5c3a8e1d9618087c5bc00f8ca5cec65a678ae2e","tid":36972,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"依啲90後真係好白痴唔識變通，我明公司規定可能唔比落閘既，咁你都要解決問題架，唔通由個問題留係度唔理咩，緊係即刻趕走班大陸人啦，港人優先唔係唔識啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a282e9d56b3380c34315311a9993ee0c24a02965","tid":36972,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好"},{"pid":"36257749e8c6feecabe3219e1a6db4b05db29a20",